<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Executive IT — Sourcing & Vendors</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap');

    :root {
      --navy: #0a192f;
      --gold: #c5a059;
      --slate: #64748b;
      --bg: #f8fafc;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --border: #e2e8f0;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--navy); display: flex; }

    /* Sidebar Corporate */
    .sidebar { width: 280px; height: 100vh; background: var(--navy); color: white; position: sticky; top: 0; padding: 40px 0; }
    .logo { padding: 0 30px 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
    .logo h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; }
    .logo span { color: var(--gold); font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; display: block; }

    .nav-item { padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; color: #cbd5e1; transition: 0.3s; border-left: 3px solid transparent; }
    .nav-item.active { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: white; border-left-color: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; }

    /* Main */
    .main { flex: 1; padding: 60px; max-width: 1300px; }
    .header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; margin-bottom: 40px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--navy); padding-bottom: 20px; }
    .header h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 32px; }

    /* Sourcing Layout */
    .panel { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .panel-title { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 25px; border-left: 3px solid var(--gold); padding-left: 15px; }

    /* Matrix 2x2 Sourcing */
    .sourcing-matrix {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 40px;
      gap: 15px;
      height: 400px;
    }
    .axis-y { writing-mode: vertical-lr; transform: rotate(180deg); text-align: center; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--slate); text-transform: uppercase; }
    .axis-x { grid-column: 2 / 4; text-align: center; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--slate); text-transform: uppercase; padding-top: 15px; }
    
    .cell { border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; }
    .cell-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    
    .q-strat { background: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.05); border-top: 4px solid var(--gold); }
    .q-secure { background: rgba(10, 25, 47, 0.02); border-top: 4px solid var(--navy); }
    .q-dev { background: rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.02); border-top: 4px solid var(--slate); }

    /* Vendor Cards */
    .vendor-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
    .vendor-card { padding: 20px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .vendor-card strong { font-size: 14px; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .vendor-card p { font-size: 12px; color: var(--slate); line-height: 1.5; }
    .crit-label { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 6px; background: var(--navy); color: white; text-transform: uppercase; }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="sidebar">
    <div class="logo">
      <h1>Executive IT</h1>
      <span>Architecture & Gouvernance</span>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-item">Vue Stratégique</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Portefeuille Apps</div>
    <div class="nav-item">TRM — Risques</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Finance IT</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Conformité & Data</div>
    <div class="nav-item">Flux & Intégration</div>
    <div class="nav-item active">Sourcing & Vendors</div>
  </nav>

  <main class="main">
    <header class="header">
      <h2>Sourcing & Vendors</h2>
      <div style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--slate);">VENDOR MANAGEMENT</div>
    </header>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-title">Qualité Fournisseur vs Criticité</div>
      <div class="sourcing-matrix">
        <div class="axis-y">Qualité de Service (SLA)</div>
        
        <div class="cell q-strat">
          <span class="cell-label" style="color: var(--gold)">Partenaires Stratégiques</span>
          <p style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--slate);">Relation à sécuriser : Haute performance, haute dépendance.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="cell q-secure">
          <span class="cell-label" style="color: var(--navy)">À Sécuriser</span>
          <p style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--slate);">Criticité élevée mais qualité de service à renforcer.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cell q-dev">
          <span class="cell-label">À Développer</span>
          <p style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--slate);">Bonne qualité mais impact stratégique encore limité.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cell">
          <span class="cell-label">À Challenger</span>
          <p style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--slate);">Faible qualité et faible valeur stratégique.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="axis-x">Criticité & Dépendance Contractuelle</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-title">Analyse de la Criticité Fournisseur</div>
      <div class="vendor-grid">
        <div class="vendor-card">
          <span class="crit-label">Continuité</span>
          <strong style="margin-top:10px;">Impact Run</strong>
          <p>Évaluation de l'impact fournisseur sur le support et les opérations critiques.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vendor-card">
          <span class="crit-label">Technique</span>
          <strong style="margin-top:10px;">Dépendance Architecture</strong>
          <p>Poids du partenaire dans les données, les interfaces ou les licences clés.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vendor-card">
          <span class="crit-label">Contractuel</span>
          <strong style="margin-top:10px;">Levier de Négociation</strong>
          <p>Capacité à diversifier ou sortir d'une relation dépendante.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
